d-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="5f1e53ad-5d2d-4cda-bf8f-cac77a0f77ec" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="164">Yes 👍 <strong data-start="7" data-end="75">AWS Skill Builder account and AWS Console account are different.</strong><br data-start="75" data-end="78">
To do your <strong data-start="89" data-end="116">S3 + CloudFront project</strong>, you need a <strong data-start="129" data-end="163">normal AWS account (Free Tier)</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="166" data-end="209">I’ll show you <strong data-start="180" data-end="208">exactly how to create it</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="211" data-end="214">
<h1 data-section-id="dvhqe9" data-start="216" data-end="248">Step 1: Go to AWS Sign-Up Page</h1>
<p data-start="249" data-end="267">Open this website:</p>
<p data-start="269" data-end="299">👉 <a data-start="272" data-end="299" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://aws.amazon.com/free">https://aws.amazon.com/free<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<p data-start="301" data-end="318">Click the button:</p>
<p data-start="320" data-end="343"><strong data-start="320" data-end="343">Create Free Account</strong></p>
<hr data-start="345" data-end="348">
<h1 data-section-id="t0cghj" data-start="350" data-end="381">Step 2: Enter Account Details</h1>
<p data-start="383" data-end="397">Fill the form:</p>
<p data-start="399" data-end="434"><strong data-start="399" data-end="416">Email address</strong><br data-start="416" data-end="419">
Use your Gmail.</p>
<p data-start="436" data-end="444">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="445" data-end="472"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>swathi123@gmail.com</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="474" data-end="514"><strong data-start="474" data-end="486">Password</strong><br data-start="486" data-end="489">
Create a strong password.</p>
<p data-start="516" data-end="536"><strong data-start="516" data-end="536">AWS account name</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="537" data-end="563"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Swathi AWS Account</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="565" data-end="595">Click <strong data-start="571" data-end="595">Verify email address</strong></p>
<p data-start="597" data-end="649">AWS will send a <strong data-start="613" data-end="648">verification code to your email</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="651" data-end="666">Enter the code.</p>
<hr data-start="668" data-end="671">
<h1 data-section-id="15e00q9" data-start="673" data-end="702">Step 3: Contact Information</h1>
<p data-start="704" data-end="711">Choose:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="713" data-end="737"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Personal Account</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="739" data-end="752">Fill details:</p>
<p data-start="754" data-end="793">Name<br data-start="758" data-end="761">
Phone number<br data-start="773" data-end="776">
Country<br data-start="783" data-end="786">
Address</p>
<p data-start="795" data-end="813">Click <strong data-start="801" data-end="813">Continue</strong></p>
<hr data-start="815" data-end="818">
<h1 data-section-id="1uoexsc" data-start="820" data-end="849">Step 4: Payment Information</h1>
<p data-start="851" data-end="896">⚠️ AWS requires <strong data-start="867" data-end="895">Debit card / Credit card</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="898" data-end="950">This is <strong data-start="906" data-end="931">only for verification</strong>, not for charging.</p>
<p data-start="952" data-end="1007">If you use <strong data-start="963" data-end="985">Free Tier services</strong>, it will cost <strong data-start="1000" data-end="1006">₹0</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1009" data-end="1015">Enter:</p>
<ul data-start="1017" data-end="1045">
<li data-section-id="1q98p3z" data-start="1017" data-end="1030">
<p data-start="1019" data-end="1030">Card number</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pd3" data-start="1031" data-end="1039">
<p data-start="1033" data-end="1039">Expiry</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o4e7f" data-start="1040" data-end="1045">
<p data-start="1042" data-end="1045">CVV</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1047" data-end="1063">Click <strong data-start="1053" data-end="1063">Verify</strong></p>
<p data-start="1065" data-end="1119">AWS may charge <strong data-start="1080" data-end="1104">₹2 or ₹5 temporarily</strong> and refund it.</p>
<hr data-start="1121" data-end="1124">
<h1 data-section-id="erfvry" data-start="1126" data-end="1154">Step 5: Phone Verification</h1>
<p data-start="1156" data-end="1175">Enter phone number.</p>
<p data-start="1177" data-end="1199">AWS will send <strong data-start="1191" data-end="1198">OTP</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1201" data-end="1211">Enter OTP.</p>
<hr data-start="1213" data-end="1216">
<h1 data-section-id="13npabd" data-start="1218" data-end="1247">Step 6: Choose Support Plan</h1>
<p data-start="1249" data-end="1256">Select:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1258" data-end="1286"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Basic Support (Free)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1288" data-end="1314">Click <strong data-start="1294" data-end="1314">Complete Sign Up</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1316" data-end="1319">
<h1 data-section-id="lzfcab" data-start="1321" data-end="1351">Step 7: Login to AWS Console</h1>
<p data-start="1353" data-end="1359">Go to:</p>
<p data-start="1361" data-end="1394">👉 <a data-start="1364" data-end="1394" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://console.aws.amazon.com/">https://console.aws.amazon.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<p data-start="1396" data-end="1402">Click:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1404" data-end="1421"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Root user</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1423" data-end="1429">Enter:</p>
<ul data-start="1431" data-end="1449">
<li data-section-id="1717an8" data-start="1431" data-end="1438">
<p data-start="1433" data-end="1438">Email</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1i84dqv" data-start="1439" data-end="1449">
<p data-start="1441" data-end="1449">Password</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1451" data-end="1509">Now you will see the <strong data-start="1472" data-end="1508">AWS Management Console dashboard</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1511" data-end="1514">
<h1 data-section-id="n6wnia" data-start="1516" data-end="1534">Important Tip ⚠️</h1>
<p data-start="1536" data-end="1568">After your project is completed:</p>
<p data-start="1570" data-end="1587">Delete resources:</p>
<ul data-start="1589" data-end="1626">
<li data-section-id="bp2fwm" data-start="1589" data-end="1600">
<p data-start="1591" data-end="1600">S3 bucket</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="r789xe" data-start="1601" data-end="1626">
<p data-start="1603" data-end="1626">CloudFront distribution</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1628" data-end="1648">This avoids charges.</p>
<hr data-start="1650" data-end="1653">
<h1 data-section-id="1lpjc6y" data-start="1655" data-end="1687">Your AWS Project Flow (Simple)</h1>
<p data-start="1689" data-end="1706">You will do this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1708" data-end="1919"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>AWS Account</span><br><span>      ↓</span><br><span>Create S3 Bucket</span><br><span>      ↓</span><br><span>Upload index.html</span><br><span>      ↓</span><br><span>Enable Static Website Hosting</span><br><span>      ↓</span><br><span>Make bucket public</span><br><span>      ↓</span><br><span>Create CloudFront</span><br><span>      ↓</span><br><span>Open website URL</span><br><span>      ↓</span><br><span>Upload to GitHub</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1921" data-end="1924">
<p data-start="1926" data-end="1962">💡 If you want, I can also give you:</p>
<p data-start="1964" data-end="2127">✔ <strong data-start="1966" data-end="2015">Ready-made website files for your AWS project</strong><br data-start="2015" data-end="2018">
✔ <strong data-start="2020" data-end="2065">Exact screenshots required for submission</strong><br data-start="2065" data-end="2068">
✔ <strong data-start="2070" data-end="2095">GitHub repo structure</strong><br data-start="2095" data-end="2098">
✔ <strong data-start="2100" data-end="2127">What to write in README</strong></p>
<p data-start="2129" data-end="2201" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Tell me and I’ll help you finish the <strong data-start="2166" data-end="2197">whole project in 30 minutes</strong>. 🚀</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><div class="text-token-text-secondary flex items-center justify-center"><button disabled="" class="hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary touch:w-[32px] flex h-[30px] w-[24px] items-center justify-center rounded-md disabled:opacity-50 disabled:hover:bg-transparent" aria-label="Previous response"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#8ee2e9" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><div class="px-0.5 text-sm font-semibold tabular-nums">1/2</div><button aria-label="Next response" class="hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary touch:w-[32px] flex h-[30px] w-[24px] items-center justify-center rounded-md disabled:opacity-50 disabled:hover:bg-transparent"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use><