flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="0cf237a7-354d-4112-b2de-e2a948aa53ab" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="124">You are on the <strong data-start="15" data-end="44">payment verification step</strong> of AWS account creation. Don’t worry — this is normal. I’ll explain what to do.</p>
<hr data-start="126" data-end="129">
<h2 data-section-id="1nvvjbi" data-start="131" data-end="154">What This Page Means</h2>
<p data-start="155" data-end="209">AWS needs a <strong data-start="167" data-end="208">payment method to verify your account</strong>.</p>
<ul data-start="211" data-end="341">
<li data-section-id="ym7y24" data-start="211" data-end="256">
<p data-start="213" data-end="256">It will charge <strong data-start="228" data-end="256">₹2 only for verification</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1cdfxgp" data-start="257" data-end="300">
<p data-start="259" data-end="300">The ₹2 will <strong data-start="271" data-end="300">automatically be refunded</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16p59ik" data-start="301" data-end="341">
<p data-start="303" data-end="341">This is just to confirm your identity.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="343" data-end="481">Your project will still use the <strong data-start="375" data-end="392">AWS Free Tier</strong>, so you should not get charged if you only use S3 and CloudFront for this small project.</p>
<hr data-start="483" data-end="486">
<h2 data-section-id="1waz72l" data-start="488" data-end="512">What You Should Enter</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1li9se2" data-start="514" data-end="528">1️⃣ UPI ID</h3>
<p data-start="529" data-end="551">Enter your <strong data-start="540" data-end="550">UPI ID</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="553" data-end="561">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="562" data-end="611"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>yourname@upi</span><br><span>yourname@okaxis</span><br><span>yourname@ybl</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="613" data-end="628">Example format:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="629" data-end="650"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>swathi123@ybl</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="652" data-end="663">Then click:</p>
<p data-start="665" data-end="691"><strong data-start="665" data-end="691">Continue (step 3 of 5)</strong></p>
<hr data-start="693" data-end="696">
<h3 data-section-id="v206l" data-start="698" data-end="721">2️⃣ Approve Payment</h3>
<p data-start="722" data-end="746">After clicking continue:</p>
<ul data-start="748" data-end="866">
<li data-section-id="ornnua" data-start="748" data-end="828">
<p data-start="750" data-end="828">You will get a <strong data-start="765" data-end="796">UPI request in your UPI app</strong> (PhonePe / Google Pay / Paytm).</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="dmhnlc" data-start="829" data-end="866">
<p data-start="831" data-end="866">Approve the <strong data-start="843" data-end="865">₹2 payment request</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="868" data-end="871">
<h3 data-section-id="1xixfuk" data-start="873" data-end="899">3️⃣ Phone Verification</h3>
<p data-start="900" data-end="927">Next step AWS will ask for:</p>
<ul data-start="929" data-end="962">
<li data-section-id="1h37kgn" data-start="929" data-end="943">
<p data-start="931" data-end="943">Phone number</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ftl9q2" data-start="944" data-end="962">
<p data-start="946" data-end="962">OTP verification</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="964" data-end="974">Enter OTP.</p>
<hr data-start="976" data-end="979">
<h3 data-section-id="1r6odeq" data-start="981" data-end="1001">4️⃣ Support Plan</h3>
<p data-start="1002" data-end="1009">Choose:</p>
<p data-start="1011" data-end="1035"><strong data-start="1011" data-end="1035">Basic Support – Free</strong></p>
<p data-start="1037" data-end="1066">Then finish account creation.</p>
<hr data-start="1068" data-end="1071">
<h2 data-section-id="1bcbhuv" data-start="1073" data-end="1086">After This</h2>
<p data-start="1087" data-end="1141">You will finally reach the <strong data-start="1114" data-end="1140">AWS Management Console</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1143" data-end="1181">From there we will start your project:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1183" data-end="1329"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>AWS Console</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>S3 Bucket</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>Upload Website</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>Enable Static Hosting</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>Make Bucket Public</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>Create CloudFront</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>Website Live</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1331" data-end="1334">
<p data-start="1336" data-end="1394">✅ <strong data-start="1338" data-end="1352">Important:</strong><br data-start="1352" data-end="1355">
After your project is reviewed, delete:</p>
<ul data-start="1396" data-end="1437">
<li data-section-id="mrpcp2" data-start="1396" data-end="1409">
<p data-start="1398" data-end="1409">S3 bucket</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tdg3m" data-start="1410" data-end="1437">
<p data-start="1412" data-end="1437">CloudFront distribution</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1439" data-end="1470">So you don’t get charged later.</p>
<hr data-start="1472" data-end="1475">
<p data-start="1477" data-end="1601">💡 If you want, I can also show you <strong data-start="1513" data-end="1589">the easiest method to finish this entire AWS project in about 20 minutes</strong>, including:</p>
<ul data-start="1602" data-end="1690" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="1bpn00d" data-start="1602" data-end="1628">
<p data-start="1604" data-end="1628">ready-made website files</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17y7wmt" data-start="1629" data-end="1657">
<p data-start="1631" data-end="1657">exact screenshots required</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wo6aao" data-start="1658" data-end="1690" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="1660" data-end="1690" data-is-last-node="">GitHub repo submission format.</p>
</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http