n></div></div></div></div><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 rounded-se-lg max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">ILA CAME</div></div></div></div><div class="text-token-text-secondary my-2 me-4 flex flex-row justify-end gap-1 text-xs"></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-WEB:c1480023-29e0-4946-9cd7-fe18d94e49f3-5" data-testid="conversation-turn-12" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant" style=""><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="b303c059-339c-4161-b701-e907df3f5caa" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="156">Perfect 👍 You have <strong data-start="20" data-end="60">successfully entered the AWS Console</strong>. Now we will start your <strong data-start="85" data-end="128">project from the beginning step-by-step</strong>. Follow exactly what I say.</p>
<p data-start="158" data-end="196">Right now you are on <strong data-start="179" data-end="195">Console Home</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="198" data-end="201">
<h1 data-section-id="ycbzgm" data-start="203" data-end="238">Step 1: Change Region (Important)</h1>
<p data-start="240" data-end="268">At the <strong data-start="247" data-end="260">top right</strong>, I see:</p>
<p data-start="270" data-end="305"><strong data-start="270" data-end="305">Europe (Stockholm) – eu-north-1</strong></p>
<p data-start="307" data-end="367">For beginners it is better to use <strong data-start="341" data-end="366">US East (N. Virginia)</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="369" data-end="406">Click the region dropdown and select:</p>
<p data-start="408" data-end="445"><strong data-start="408" data-end="445">US East (N. Virginia) – us-east-1</strong></p>
<p data-start="447" data-end="493">(CloudFront and tutorials work smoothly here.)</p>
<hr data-start="495" data-end="498">
<h1 data-section-id="14fxqiw" data-start="500" data-end="517">Step 2: Open S3</h1>
<p data-start="519" data-end="551">At the <strong data-start="526" data-end="544">top search bar</strong>, type:</p>
<p data-start="553" data-end="559"><strong data-start="553" data-end="559">S3</strong></p>
<p data-start="561" data-end="572">Then click:</p>
<p data-start="574" data-end="587"><strong data-start="574" data-end="587">Amazon S3</strong></p>
<p data-start="589" data-end="635">S3 is where your website files will be stored.</p>
<hr data-start="637" data-end="640">
<h1 data-section-id="o5tafr" data-start="642" data-end="668">Step 3: Create S3 Bucket</h1>
<p data-start="670" data-end="687">Click the button:</p>
<p data-start="689" data-end="706"><strong data-start="689" data-end="706">Create bucket</strong></p>
<p data-start="708" data-end="722">Fill the form.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1su2yjz" data-start="724" data-end="739">Bucket name</h3>
<p data-start="740" data-end="767">Type something unique like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="769" data-end="803"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>swathi-static-website-2026</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="805" data-end="837">(If error appears, add numbers.)</p>
<h3 data-section-id="pjsx32" data-start="839" data-end="849">Region</h3>
<p data-start="850" data-end="855">Keep:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="857" data-end="886"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>US East (N. Virginia)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-section-id="lh27bm" data-start="888" data-end="906">Important Step</h3>
<p data-start="908" data-end="923">Scroll down to:</p>
<p data-start="925" data-end="957"><strong data-start="925" data-end="957">Block Public Access settings</strong></p>
<p data-start="959" data-end="967">Uncheck:</p>
<p data-start="969" data-end="998">✔ <strong data-start="971" data-end="998">Block all public access</strong></p>
<p data-start="1000" data-end="1036">Then check the warning confirmation.</p>
<p data-start="1038" data-end="1044">Click:</p>
<p data-start="1046" data-end="1063"><strong data-start="1046" data-end="1063">Create bucket</strong></p>
<p data-start="1065" data-end="1093">Your bucket will be created.</p>
<hr data-start="1095" data-end="1098">
<h1 data-section-id="1fsz18k" data-start="1100" data-end="1129">Step 4: Upload Website File</h1>
<p data-start="1131" data-end="1158">Click your <strong data-start="1142" data-end="1157">bucket name</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1160" data-end="1166">Click:</p>
<p data-start="1168" data-end="1178"><strong data-start="1168" data-end="1178">Upload</strong></p>
<p data-start="1180" data-end="1185">Then:</p>
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1200"><strong data-start="1187" data-end="1200">Add files</strong></p>
<p data-start="1202" data-end="1209">Upload:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1211" data-end="1229"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1231" data-end="1237">Click:</p>
<p data-start="1239" data-end="1249"><strong data-start="1239" data-end="1249">Upload</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1251" data-end="1254">
<h1 data-section-id="9n5xfd" data-start="1256" data-end="1295">Step 5: Enable Static Website Hosting</h1>
<p data-start="1297" data-end="1315">Inside the bucket:</p>
<p data-start="1317" data-end="1327">Click tab:</p>
<p data-start="1329" data-end="1343"><strong data-start="1329" data-end="1343">Properties</strong></p>
<p data-start="1345" data-end="1360">Scroll down to:</p>
<p data-start="1362" data-end="1388"><strong data-start="1362" data-end="1388">Static website hosting</strong></p>
<p data-start="1390" data-end="1396">Click:</p>
<p data-start="1398" data-end="1406"><strong data-start="1398" data-end="1406">Edit</strong></p>
<p data-start="1408" data-end="1415">Select:</p>
<p data-start="1417" data-end="1427"><strong data-start="1417" data-end="1427">Enable</strong></p>
<p data-start="1429" data-end="1444">Index document:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1446" data-end="1464"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1466" data-end="1472">Click:</p>
<p data-start="1474" data-end="1490"><strong data-start="1474" data-end="1490">Save changes</strong></p>
<p data-start="1492" data-end="1537">Now AWS will give a <strong data-start="1512" data-end="1536">Website endpoint URL</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1539" data-end="1547">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1549" data-end="1625"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>http://swathi-static-website-2026.s3-website-us-east-1.amazonaws.com</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1627" data-end="1641">Save this URL.</p>
<hr data-start="1643" data-end="1646">
<h1 data-section-id="ei20ut" data-start="1648" data-end="1676">Step 6: Make Bucket Public</h1>
<p data-start="1678" data-end="1684">Click:</p>
<p data-start="1686" data-end="1701"><strong data-start="1686" data-end="1701">Permissions</strong></p>
<p data-start="1703" data-end="1713">Scroll to:</p>
<p data-start="1715" data-end="1732"><strong data-start="1715" data-end="1732">Bucket Policy</strong></p>
<p data-start="1734" data-end="1759">Click <strong data-start="1740" data-end="1748">Edit</strong> and paste:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1761" data-end="1984"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>{</span><br><span> "Version":</span><span class="ͼc">"2012-10-17"</span><span>,</span><br><span> "Statement":[{</span><br><span>   "Sid":</span><span class="ͼc">"PublicReadGetObject"</span><span>,</span><br><span>   "Effect":</span><span class="ͼc">"Allow"</span><span>,</span><br><span>   "Principal":</span><span class="ͼc">"*"</span><span>,</span><br><span>   "Action":[</span><span class="ͼc">"s3:GetObject"</span><span>],</span><br><span>   "Resource":[</span><span class="ͼc">"arn:aws:s3:::swathi-static-website-2026/*"</span><span>]</span><br><span> }]</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1986" data-end="2001">Click <strong data-start="1992" data-end="2000">Save</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="2003" data-end="2039">Now your website becomes <strong data-start="2028" data-end="2038">public</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2041" data-end="2044">
<h1 data-section-id="17ogaus" data-start="2046" data-end="2068">Step 7: Test Website</h1>
<p data-start="2070" data-end="2118">Open the <strong data-start="2079" data-end="2106">S3 Website Endpoint URL</strong> in browser.</p>
<p data-start="2120" data-end="2145">Your website will appear.</p>
<p data-start="2147" data-end="2163">Take screenshot.</p>
<hr data-start="2165" data-end="2168">
<h1 data-section-id="td8kw2" data-start="2170" data-end="2197">Step 8: Create CloudFront</h1>
<p data-start="2199" data-end="2224">Search in AWS search bar:</p>
<p data-start="2226" data-end="2240"><strong data-start="2226" data-end="2240">CloudFront</strong></p>
<p data-start="2242" data-end="2248">Click:</p>
<p data-start="2250" data-end="2273"><strong data-start="2250" data-end="2273">Create Distribution</strong></p>
<p data-start="2275" data-end="2289">Origin domain:</p>
<p data-start="2291" data-end="2317">Select your <strong data-start="2303" data-end="2316">S3 bucket</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="2319" data-end="2344">Leave everything default.</p>
<p data-start="2346" data-end="2352">Click:</p>
<p data-start="2354" data-end="2377"><strong data-start="2354" data-end="2377">Create distribution</strong></p>
<p data-start="2379" data-end="2401">Wait <strong data-start="2384" data-end="2400">5–10 minutes</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="2403" data-end="2450">You will get a <strong data-start="2418" data-end="2444">CloudFront domain name</strong> like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2452" data-end="2492"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://d3abcd123.cloudfront.net</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2494" data-end="2513">Open it in browser.</p>
<p data-start="2515" data-end="2531">Take screenshot.</p>
<hr data-start="2533" data-end="2536">
<h1 data-section-id="1ct2vb2" data-start="2538" data-end="2566">Step 9: Prepare Submission</h1>
<p data-start="2568" data-end="2584">You must submit:</p>
<p data-start="2586" data-end="2601"><strong data-start="2586" data-end="2601">Screenshots</strong></p>
<p data-start="2603" data-end="2750">1️⃣ S3 bucket created<br data-start="2624" data-end="2627">
2️⃣ Website files uploaded<br data-start="2653" data-end="2656">
3️⃣ Static hosting enabled<br data-start="2682" data-end="2685">
4️⃣ Website working in browser<br data-start="2715" data-end="2718">
5️⃣ CloudFront distribution page</p>
<p data-start="2752" data-end="2763">And create:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2765" data-end="2783"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>README.txt</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2785" data-end="2788">
<h1 data-section-id="8gflp3" data-start="2790" data-end="2817">Your Project Architecture</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2819" data-end="2939"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span><br><span>     ↓</span><br><span>Amazon S3 Bucket</span><br><span>     ↓</span><br><span>Static Website Hosting</span><br><span>     ↓</span><br><span>CloudFront CDN</span><br><span>     ↓</span><br><span>Public Website URL</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2941" data-end="2944">
