<p data-start="54" data-end="73">Right now it shows:</p>
<p data-start="75" data-end="115"><strong data-start="75" data-end="115">S3 static website hosting → Disabled</strong></p>
<p data-start="117" data-end="142">We need to <strong data-start="128" data-end="141">enable it</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="144" data-end="147">
<h1 data-section-id="iger71" data-start="149" data-end="173">Step 1: Click <strong data-start="165" data-end="173">Edit</strong></h1>
<p data-start="175" data-end="230">On the right side of <strong data-start="196" data-end="222">Static website hosting</strong>, click:</p>
<p data-start="232" data-end="240"><strong data-start="232" data-end="240">Edit</strong></p>
<hr data-start="242" data-end="245">
<h1 data-section-id="n0ow9q" data-start="247" data-end="286">Step 2: Enable Static Website Hosting</h1>
<p data-start="288" data-end="318">A new settings page will open.</p>
<p data-start="320" data-end="327">Select:</p>
<p data-start="329" data-end="341">✔ <strong data-start="331" data-end="341">Enable</strong></p>
<p data-start="343" data-end="355">Then choose:</p>
<p data-start="357" data-end="373"><strong data-start="357" data-end="373">Hosting type</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="375" data-end="416"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Host a static website</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="418" data-end="421">
<h1 data-section-id="5tycdg" data-start="423" data-end="453">Step 3: Enter Index Document</h1>
<p data-start="455" data-end="483">In <strong data-start="458" data-end="476">Index document</strong>, type:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="485" data-end="515"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="517" data-end="548">Leave <strong data-start="523" data-end="541">Error document</strong> empty.</p>
<hr data-start="550" data-end="553">
<h1 data-section-id="4ya9jv" data-start="555" data-end="569">Step 4: Save</h1>
<p data-start="571" data-end="593">Scroll down and click:</p>
<p data-start="595" data-end="611"><strong data-start="595" data-end="611">Save changes</strong></p>
<hr data-start="613" data-end="616">
<h1 data-section-id="1ajvbbi" data-start="618" data-end="644">Step 5: Copy Website URL</h1>
<p data-start="646" data-end="706">After saving, AWS will show a <strong data-start="676" data-end="700">Website endpoint URL</strong> like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="708" data-end="796"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>http://swathi-static-website-2026.s3-website-us-east-1.amazonaws.com</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="798" data-end="828">This is your <strong data-start="811" data-end="827">website link</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="830" data-end="833">
<h1 data-section-id="1wcamz9" data-start="835" data-end="856">Next Important Step</h1>
<p data-start="857" data-end="947">Now we must <strong data-start="869" data-end="895">make the bucket public</strong>, otherwise the website will show <strong data-start="929" data-end="946">Access Denied</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="949" data-end="968">Next we will go to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="970" data-end="1005"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Permissions tab</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1007" data-end="1035">and add a <strong data-start="1017" data-end="1034">Bucket Policy</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1037" data-end="1040">
<p data-start="1042" data-end="1145" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">📩 Send the <strong data-start="1054" data-end="1094">next screenshot after you click Save</strong>, and I will guide you to the <strong data-start="1124" data-end="1144">Permissions step</strong>.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><b