<p data-start="21" data-end="84"><strong data-start="21" data-end="65">Uncheck means removing the tick mark (✓)</strong> from the checkbox.</p>
<p data-start="86" data-end="184">In your screen all the boxes are <strong data-start="119" data-end="140">already unchecked</strong>, which is exactly what we want. Good job! ✅</p>
<p data-start="186" data-end="207">Now do the next step.</p>
<hr data-start="209" data-end="212">
<h1 data-section-id="1ozjkej" data-start="214" data-end="236">Step 1: Save Changes</h1>
<p data-start="238" data-end="281">Scroll <strong data-start="245" data-end="267">down to the bottom</strong> of this page.</p>
<p data-start="283" data-end="300">Click the button:</p>
<p data-start="302" data-end="318"><strong data-start="302" data-end="318">Save changes</strong></p>
<p data-start="320" data-end="362">AWS will show a popup asking confirmation.</p>
<p data-start="364" data-end="369">Type:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="371" data-end="398"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>confirm</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="400" data-end="411">Then click:</p>
<p data-start="413" data-end="424"><strong data-start="413" data-end="424">Confirm</strong></p>
<p data-start="426" data-end="471">Now <strong data-start="430" data-end="470">Block Public Access will be disabled</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="473" data-end="476">
<h1 data-section-id="1ptdewj" data-start="478" data-end="505">Step 2: Add Bucket Policy</h1>
<p data-start="507" data-end="556">After saving, go back to the <strong data-start="536" data-end="555">Permissions tab</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="558" data-end="573">Scroll down to:</p>
<p data-start="575" data-end="592"><strong data-start="575" data-end="592">Bucket Policy</strong></p>
<p data-start="594" data-end="600">Click:</p>
<p data-start="602" data-end="610"><strong data-start="602" data-end="610">Edit</strong></p>
<p data-start="612" data-end="630">Paste this policy:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="632" data-end="867"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>{</span><br><span> "Version":</span><span class="ͼc">"2012-10-17"</span><span>,</span><br><span> "Statement":[{</span><br><span>   "Sid":</span><span class="ͼc">"PublicReadGetObject"</span><span>,</span><br><span>   "Effect":</span><span class="ͼc">"Allow"</span><span>,</span><br><span>   "Principal":</span><span class="ͼc">"*"</span><span>,</span><br><span>   "Action":[</span><span class="ͼc">"s3:GetObject"</span><span>],</span><br><span>   "Resource":[</span><span class="ͼc">"arn:aws:s3:::swathi-static-website-2026/*"</span><span>]</span><br><span> }]</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="869" data-end="880">Then click:</p>
<p data-start="882" data-end="898"><strong data-start="882" data-end="898">Save changes</strong></p>
<hr data-start="900" data-end="903">
<h1 data-section-id="17tvufm" data-start="905" data-end="927">Step 3: Open Website</h1>
<p data-start="929" data-end="939">Now go to:</p>
<p data-start="941" data-end="980"><strong data-start="941" data-end="980">Properties → Static website hosting</strong></p>
<p data-start="982" data-end="1016">Copy the <strong data-start="991" data-end="1015">Website endpoint URL</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1018" data-end="1026">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1028" data-end="1116"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>http://swathi-static-website-2026.s3-website-us-east-1.amazonaws.com</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1118" data-end="1138">Paste it in browser.</p>
<p data-start="1140" data-end="1155">You should see:</p>
<p data-start="1157" data-end="1186"><strong data-start="1157" data-end="1186">Welcome to My Travel Blog</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1188" data-end="1191">
<p data-start="1193" data-end="1316" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">📩 After you click <strong data-start="1212" data-end="1228">Save changes</strong>, send the next screenshot and we will finish the <strong data-start="1278" data-end="1312">CloudFront part of the project</strong>. 🚀</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg