Most of the fields here can stay <strong data-start="102" data-end="113">default</strong>, so follow these steps carefully.</p>
<hr data-start="149" data-end="152">
<h1 data-section-id="vo5uqq" data-start="154" data-end="181">Step 1: Distribution Name</h1>
<p data-start="183" data-end="236">In <strong data-start="186" data-end="207">Distribution name</strong>, type something simple like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="238" data-end="267"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>swathi-static-website</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="269" data-end="290">This is just a label.</p>
<hr data-start="292" data-end="295">
<h1 data-section-id="1kctvzp" data-start="297" data-end="329">Step 2: Description (Optional)</h1>
<p data-start="331" data-end="344">You can type:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="346" data-end="381"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Static website hosted on S3</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="383" data-end="401">Or leave it empty.</p>
<hr data-start="403" data-end="406">
<h1 data-section-id="1m4zy8v" data-start="408" data-end="435">Step 3: Distribution Type</h1>
<p data-start="437" data-end="458">You already selected:</p>
<p data-start="460" data-end="487">✅ <strong data-start="462" data-end="487">Single website or app</strong></p>
<p data-start="489" data-end="508">Leave it like that.</p>
<hr data-start="510" data-end="513">
<h1 data-section-id="zniqs3" data-start="515" data-end="539">Step 4: Domain Section</h1>
<p data-start="541" data-end="587">You see <strong data-start="549" data-end="587">Route 53 managed domain – optional</strong></p>
<p data-start="589" data-end="657">⚠️ <strong data-start="592" data-end="612">Leave this empty</strong>.<br data-start="613" data-end="616">
You don’t need a domain for this project.</p>
<hr data-start="659" data-end="662">
<h1 data-section-id="l356h7" data-start="664" data-end="695">Step 5: Scroll Down to Origin</h1>
<p data-start="697" data-end="751">Keep scrolling down until you see <strong data-start="731" data-end="741">Origin</strong> settings.</p>
<p data-start="753" data-end="807">In <strong data-start="756" data-end="773">Origin domain</strong>, choose your S3 website endpoint.</p>
<p data-start="809" data-end="827">It will look like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="829" data-end="898"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>swathi-static-website-2026.s3-website-us-east-1.amazonaws.com</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="900" data-end="970">Make sure you pick the <strong data-start="923" data-end="943">website endpoint</strong>, not just the bucket name.</p>
<hr data-start="972" data-end="975">
<h1 data-section-id="1b91pee" data-start="977" data-end="1003">Step 6: Default Settings</h1>
<p data-start="1005" data-end="1038">Leave everything else as default:</p>
<ul data-start="1040" data-end="1159">
<li data-section-id="au2oby" data-start="1040" data-end="1083">
<p data-start="1042" data-end="1083">Viewer protocol policy → HTTP and HTTPS</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1d5rky2" data-start="1084" data-end="1127">
<p data-start="1086" data-end="1127">Cache policy → Managed-CachingOptimized</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sca1y4" data-start="1128" data-end="1159">
<p data-start="1130" data-end="1159">Allowed methods → GET, HEAD</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1161" data-end="1164">
<h1 data-section-id="19fxqmf" data-start="1166" data-end="1195">Step 7: Create Distribution</h1>
<p data-start="1197" data-end="1228">Scroll to the bottom and click:</p>
<p data-start="1230" data-end="1253"><strong data-start="1230" data-end="1253">Create distribution</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1255" data-end="1258">
<h1 data-section-id="1srmom7" data-start="1260" data-end="1289">Step 8: Wait for Deployment</h1>
<p data-start="1291" data-end="1312">CloudFront will show:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1314" data-end="1339"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Status: Deploying</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1341" data-end="1389">Wait about <strong data-start="1352" data-end="1368">5–10 minutes</strong> until it changes to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1391" data-end="1407"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Deployed</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1409" data-end="1412">
<h1 data-section-id="qmttw8" data-start="1414" data-end="1443">Step 9: Open CloudFront URL</h1>
<p data-start="1445" data-end="1481">You will get a <strong data-start="1460" data-end="1475">Domain name</strong> like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1483" data-end="1517"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>d3abc123xyz.cloudfront.net</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1519" data-end="1543">Open it in your browser.</p>
<p data-start="1545" data-end="1590">Your <strong data-start="1550" data-end="1573">Travel Blog website</strong> will load again.</p>
<hr data-start="1592" data-end="1595">
<h1 data-section-id="1ca7kq5" data-start="1597" data-end="1638">Final Screenshots Needed for Submission</h1>
<p data-start="1640" data-end="1660">Take screenshots of:</p>
<p data-start="1662" data-end="1815">1️⃣ S3 bucket created<br data-start="1683" data-end="1686">
2️⃣ index.html uploaded<br data-start="1709" data-end="1712">
3️⃣ Static website hosting enabled<br data-start="1746" data-end="1749">
4️⃣ Website opened in browser<br data-start="1778" data-end="1781">
5️⃣ CloudFront distribution page</p>
<hr data-start="1817" data-end="1820">
<p data-start="1822" data-end="1860">If you want, I can also help you with:</p>
<p data-start="1862" data-end="1995">✅ <strong data-start="1864" data-end="1907">Exact README.txt content for submission</strong><br data-start="1907" data-end="1910">
✅ <strong data-start="1912" data-end="1947">How to submit GitHub repository</strong><br data-start="1947" data-end="1950">
✅ <strong data-start="1952" data-end="1995">How to zip the project folder correctly</strong></p>
<p data-start="1997" data-end="2012" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Just tell me 👍</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state