events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-WEB:c1480023-29e0-4946-9cd7-fe18d94e49f3-17" data-testid="conversation-turn-36" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant" style=""><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="6f648e28-9eb9-454c-b48e-6417c7f0b621" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="94">Great 👍 You selected the bucket correctly. You just need to do <strong data-start="64" data-end="93">one small important thing</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="96" data-end="129">Right now AWS shows this warning:</p>
<blockquote data-start="131" data-end="210">
<p data-start="133" data-end="210"><em data-start="133" data-end="210">This S3 bucket has static web hosting enabled… use the S3 website endpoint.</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="212" data-end="252">So we must click the recommended option.</p>
<hr data-start="254" data-end="257">
<h1 data-section-id="1tw13re" data-start="259" data-end="299">Step 1: Click <strong data-start="275" data-end="299">Use website endpoint</strong></h1>
<p data-start="301" data-end="345">On the right side of the warning box, click:</p>
<p data-start="347" data-end="371"><strong data-start="347" data-end="371">Use website endpoint</strong></p>
<p data-start="373" data-end="419">Then the origin will change to something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="421" data-end="490"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>swathi-static-website-2026.s3-website-us-east-1.amazonaws.com</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="492" data-end="528">This is correct for static websites.</p>
<hr data-start="530" data-end="533">
<h1 data-section-id="1f5zbt9" data-start="535" data-end="573">Step 2: Leave Other Settings Default</h1>
<p data-start="575" data-end="595">Do not change these:</p>
<ul data-start="597" data-end="746">
<li data-section-id="1ri1mr1" data-start="597" data-end="626">
<p data-start="599" data-end="626">Origin path → leave empty</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="au2oby" data-start="627" data-end="670">
<p data-start="629" data-end="670">Viewer protocol policy → HTTP and HTTPS</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1d5rky2" data-start="671" data-end="714">
<p data-start="673" data-end="714">Cache policy → Managed-CachingOptimized</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sca1y4" data-start="715" data-end="746">
<p data-start="717" data-end="746">Allowed methods → GET, HEAD</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="748" data-end="751">
<h1 data-section-id="1xyo5mr" data-start="753" data-end="782">Step 3: Create Distribution</h1>
<p data-start="784" data-end="812">Scroll <strong data-start="791" data-end="811">all the way down</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="814" data-end="820">Click:</p>
<p data-start="822" data-end="845"><strong data-start="822" data-end="845">Create distribution</strong></p>
<hr data-start="847" data-end="850">
<h1 data-section-id="3kq6j7" data-start="852" data-end="881">Step 4: Wait for Deployment</h1>
<p data-start="883" data-end="904">CloudFront will show:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="906" data-end="931"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Status: Deploying</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="933" data-end="978">Wait about <strong data-start="944" data-end="960">5–10 minutes</strong> until it becomes:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="980" data-end="996"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Deployed</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="998" data-end="1001">
<h1 data-section-id="wz5ero" data-start="1003" data-end="1036">Step 5: Open CloudFront Website</h1>
<p data-start="1038" data-end="1074">You will get a <strong data-start="1053" data-end="1068">Domain Name</strong> like:</p>
