<h1 data-section-id="12s6qzv" data-start="248" data-end="289">What Just Happened (Simple Explanation)</h1>
<p data-start="291" data-end="339">You built a <strong data-start="303" data-end="338">real cloud website architecture</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="341" data-end="379">Your website flow now works like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="381" data-end="607"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html (your website file)</span><br><span>        ↓</span><br><span>Amazon S3 Bucket (stores website files)</span><br><span>        ↓</span><br><span>Static Website Hosting enabled</span><br><span>        ↓</span><br><span>CloudFront CDN (faster global delivery)</span><br><span>        ↓</span><br><span>Public website link opens in browser</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="609" data-end="651">So when someone opens the CloudFront link:</p>
<p data-start="653" data-end="803">1️⃣ The request goes to <strong data-start="677" data-end="691">CloudFront</strong><br data-start="691" data-end="694">
2️⃣ CloudFront fetches the file from <strong data-start="731" data-end="744">S3 bucket</strong><br data-start="744" data-end="747">
3️⃣ CloudFront delivers the website <strong data-start="783" data-end="803">faster worldwide</strong></p>
<hr data-start="805" data-end="808">
<h1 data-section-id="1c1woma" data-start="810" data-end="850">This Means Your Project Is Completed ✅</h1>
<p data-start="852" data-end="873">You successfully did:</p>
<p data-start="875" data-end="1056">✔ Created S3 bucket<br data-start="894" data-end="897">
✔ Uploaded website files<br data-start="921" data-end="924">
✔ Enabled static website hosting<br data-start="956" data-end="959">
✔ Configured public access<br data-start="985" data-end="988">
✔ Created CloudFront distribution<br data-start="1021" data-end="1024">
✔ Website accessible on internet</p>
<p data-start="1058" data-end="1103">That is exactly what the <strong data-start="1083" data-end="1102">rubric required</strong>.</p>
