png</code>.</strong></p>
<p data-start="74" data-end="131">It clearly shows the important things reviewers look for:</p>
<p data-start="133" data-end="274">✅ <strong data-start="135" data-end="165">CloudFront Distribution ID</strong><br data-start="165" data-end="168">
✅ <strong data-start="170" data-end="190">Status = Enabled</strong><br data-start="190" data-end="193">
✅ <strong data-start="195" data-end="214">Type = Standard</strong><br data-start="214" data-end="217">
✅ <strong data-start="219" data-end="242">Domain name visible</strong><br data-start="242" data-end="245">
✅ <strong data-start="247" data-end="274">Origin = your S3 bucket</strong></p>
<p data-start="276" data-end="335">That means it proves <strong data-start="297" data-end="334">CloudFront is created and working</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="337" data-end="340">
<h2 data-section-id="aq3j9z" data-start="342" data-end="364">Name the Screenshot</h2>
