<p data-start="1492" data-end="1566">⚠️ <strong data-start="1495" data-end="1517">One last reminder:</strong><br data-start="1517" data-end="1520">
After your project review is finished, delete:</p>
<p data-start="1568" data-end="1609">• S3 bucket<br data-start="1579" data-end="1582">
• CloudFront distribution</p>
