<p data-start="1045" data-end="1076">to the project submission page.</p>
<hr data-start="1078" data-end="1081">
<p data-start="1083" data-end="1176">✅ At this point your <strong data-start="1104" data-end="1175">AWS Static Website Deployment project is fully complete and correct</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1178" data-end="1181">
<p data-start="1183" data-end="1242">⚠️ After your project gets <strong data-start="1210" data-end="1233">reviewed and passed</strong>, delete:</p>
<p data-start="1244" data-end="1285">• S3 bucket<br data-start="1255" data-end="1258">
• CloudFront distribution</p>
<p data-start="1287" data-end="1308">to avoid AWS billing.</p>
<hr data-start="1310" data-end="1313">
